  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个OTT教育场景的状态流转图。用户从GradeSync系统进入，先建立连接，然后可以选择创建房间或者加入已有房间，最后在房间里使用OTT观看教学视频，视频流由ClassroomService提供。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是GradeSync，然后用户连上OTT。我想确认一下：创建房间和加入房间这两个操作，是互斥选择还是可以先后发生？比如用户必须先创建才能加入，还是可以直接加入别人的房间？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "两者都可以从连接状态直接发起。不过实际场景里，如果用户创建了房间，通常紧接着会自己加入这个房间——所以CreateRoom到JoinRoom应该有一条流转线。当然用户也可以直接JoinRoom，跳过创建。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Connect分出两条线到CreateRoom和JoinRoom，同时CreateRoom再到JoinRoom。那UseOTT这个状态呢？是在JoinRoom之后才能开始看视频对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，必须先加入房间才能UseOTT。UseOTT之后，视频内容实际是由Education_ClassroomService提供的，所以最后要指向ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。我检查一下：GradeSync作为外部系统触发Connect，Connect可以走到CreateRoom或JoinRoom，CreateRoom也能走到JoinRoom，JoinRoom之后进入UseOTT看视频，最后UseOTT指向ClassroomService获取内容。结构应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
